(10080, 'JA News Pro! Module', 'module', 'mod_janewspro', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, '{"legacy":false,"name":"JA News Pro! Module","type":"module","creationDate":"November 2011","author":"JoomlArt.com","copyright":"J.O.O.M Solutions Co., Ltd.","authorEmail":"webmaster@joomlart.com","authorUrl":"www.joomlart.com","version":"1.1.1","description":"\\n\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h1>Introduce<\\/h1>\\n\\t\\t\\t<span style=\\"color: #008000;\\">JA NEWS PRO Module comes with rich backend and advanced features for easy configuration.<\\/strong><\\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><span style=\\"color: #ff6600;\\"><strong>Features:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\tIt lets you manage news on frontpage more professionally.\\n\\t\\t\\t<img border=\\"0\\" alt=\\"JA Highslide plugin\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/asset.joomlart.com\\/images\\/stories\\/extensions\\/joomla\\/jaec_highslide.png?javer=1109130907\\" style=\\"float: left\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><strong><span style=\\"color: #ff0000;\\">Important Instructions:<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\tJA NEWSPRO support K2 and Joomla Content and User setting in front end\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><strong><span style=\\"color: #ff0000;\\">Usage Instructions:<\\/span><br \\/><\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\tJA News Pro module easy configuration with K2 component and Joomla Content<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\tJA News Pro module support 4 theme and allow user front end config content which is displayed in module ( User Setting Tool )<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\tJA News Pro module compatiable with JA Teline IV template<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><strong><span style=\\"color: #ff0000;\\">Upgrade Methods:<\\/span><br \\/><\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<ol><li>Standard joomla uninstall \\/ reinstall method. Module supports upgrade method. <\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>You can install new version directly over this version. Uninstallation is not required. <\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\t<li>Backup any customized file before upgrading, your settings would be saved though.<\\/li><\\/ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><span style=\\"color: #008000;\\"><strong>Links:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<ul><li><a target=\\"_blank\\" href=\\"http:\\/\\/update.joomlart.com\\/#products.list\\/module_16\\/JA%20News%20Pro%20module%20for%20Joomla%201.7\\/\\">Updates &amp; Versions<\\/a><\\/li><\\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p>Copyright 2004 - 2011 <a href=\\"http:\\/\\/www.joomlart.com\\/\\" title=\\"Visit Joomlart.com!\\">JoomlArt.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\n\\t","group":""}', '{"moduleclass_sfx":"","settingcontent":"","source":"JANewsHelper","getChildren":"1","catsid":"","k2catsid":"","groupbysubcat":"0","maxSubCats":"-1","featured":"hide","ordering":"ordering","sort_order":"DESC","timerange":"","settingprofile":"","profile":"default","JPlugins":"1","K2Plugins":"1","colors":"","jacache":"1","jacache_time":"900"}', '', '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 0, 0),
(10005, 'JA Content Slider', 'module', 'mod_jacontentslider', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, '{"legacy":false,"name":"JA Content Slider","type":"module","creationDate":"December 2011","author":"JoomlArt.com","copyright":"Copyright (C), J.O.O.M Solutions Co., Ltd. All Rights Reserved.","authorEmail":"webmaster@joomlart.com","authorUrl":"www.joomlart.com","version":"1.1.8","description":"\\n\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<h1>Introduce<\\/h1>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div style=''font-weight:normal''>\\n\\t\\t\\t<span style=''color: #008000;''>Slide your contents with images from folder, category or many categories.<\\/strong><\\/span><br\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\tSlide your articles from Joomla! categories with cool effects, rich backend configs covering layout, animation control, auto thumbnail creation, images size, number of articles, sorting & much more... <br\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<br\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><span style=''color: #ff6600;''><strong>Features:<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<img border=''0'' alt=''JA Highslide plugin'' src=''http:\\/\\/asset.joomlart.com\\/images\\/stories\\/extensions\\/joomla\\/ja_contentslider.png?javer=1109280907'' style=''float: left''>This module will display your content in a slide. Its will slide one per one content with your direction.When you move your mouse over the image beside slide, The slide''s direction will change with that direction in image and slide will move faster. Then, when you move your mouse out the image, the slide will keep new direction and the slide will move with old speed.<br\\/><br\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><strong><span style=''color: #ff0000;''>Important Instructions:<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\tCheck in your configuration in your site if there isn''t this line \\"var $absolute_path by ''your absulute path'';\\" you have to add its there to run.<br \\/><br\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><strong><span style=''color: #ff0000;''>Usage Instructions:<\\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<ul style=\\"font-weight:normal\\">\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- Slide your content with your width and height properties.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- You can set the number of content will display in a tab.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- You can set the categories contents will display.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- You can set display title, link title, introtext, read more text links or not.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- You can set the slide to auto run or not. Default is yes.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- Set direction of slide. Default is left.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- Set to use zip javascript file or not. You should chose yes for this option.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>- And the last is set time for rolling delay time and animation time.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><strong><span style=''color: #ff0000;''>Upgrade Methods:<\\/span>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <\\/strong><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Standard joomla uninstall \\/ reinstall method. Module supports upgrade method. <\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>You can install new version directly over this version. Uninstallation is not required. <\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Backup any customized file before upgrading, your settings would be saved though.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><span style=''color: #008000;''><strong>Links :<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li><a target=''_blank'' href=''http:\\/\\/update.joomlart.com\\/#products.list\\/module_16\\/JA Contenslider module for Joomla 1.7\\/''>Updates &amp; Versions<\\/a><\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/ul>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p>Copyright 2004 - 2011 <a href=''http:\\/\\/www.joomlart.com\\/'' title=''Visit Joomlart.com!''>JoomlArt.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\n\\t","group":""}', '{"moduleclass_sfx":"","settingcontent":"","source":"content","folder_images":"","catid":"","k2catsid":"","text_heading":"","showTab":"1","sort_order_field":"created","sort_order":"DESC","numElem":"3","maxitems":"10","link_titles":"1","showimages":"1","iwidth":"130","iheight":"90","showreadmore":"0","showi