(10086, 'JA Side News', 'module', 'mod_jasidenews', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, '{"legacy":false,"name":"JA Side News","type":"module","creationDate":"19 October 2011","author":"Joomlart.com","copyright":"Copyright (C), J.O.O.M Solutions Co., Ltd. All Rights Reserved.","authorEmail":"webmaster@joomlart.com","authorUrl":"http:\\/\\/www.joomlart.com","version":"1.2.3","description":"\\n\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<span style=\\"color: #008000;\\"><strong>JA Side News Module<\\/strong><\\/span><br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<p><img alt=\\"JA Side News Module\\" src=\\"http:\\/\\/static.joomlart.com\\/images\\/stories\\/extensions\\/joomla\\/ja_sidenews.png\\" \\/><\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t<div style=\\"font-weight:normal\\">\\n\\t\\t\\tJA Side News module allows to display a list of articles with meta keyword ''''Featured'''' (this word is declared in the ''''Keyword'''' param inside the Metadata Information of each article).\\n\\t\\t\\t<p>Otherwise, it displays articles from one or many categories. The list can be sorted by Date, Order or Hits.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t\\t<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<span style=\\"color: #ff6600;\\"><strong>Features:<\\/strong><\\/span><br\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>2 display layouts to choose from.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Configure image sizes, dates and even read more button.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Choose sidenews layout for text overlay effect.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Easy to configure colors for overlay, text. Animation control with easy dimensions.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t<br \\/><br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<strong><span style=\\"color: #ff0000;\\">Important Instructions:<\\/span><\\/strong><br \\/>\\n\\n\\t\\t\\t<ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Keep your module updated with the latest version<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t<\\/ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<br \\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<strong><span style=\\"color: #ff0000;\\">Upgrade Methods:<\\/span><\\/strong><br \\/>\\n\\n\\t\\t\\t<ol>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Standard joomla uninstall \\/ reinstall method. OR<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t\\t  <li>Module s